{"data":{"id":"ChIJsd8Recb2BFMRgtZcHAsmc9Q","types":["restaurant","bistro","catering_service","food_delivery","cafe","grocery_store","market","bakery","food_store","store","food","service","point_of_interest","establishment"],"nationalPhoneNumber":"(306) 933-3021","internationalPhoneNumber":"+1 306-933-3021","formattedAddress":"245 3 Ave S, Saskatoon, SK S7K 1M4, Canada","rating":4.7,"websiteUri":"http://livingskycafe.com/","regularOpeningHours":{"openNow":false,"periods":[{"open":{"day":0,"hour":9,"minute":0},"close":{"day":0,"hour":15,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":1,"hour":9,"minute":0},"close":{"day":1,"hour":15,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":2,"hour":9,"minute":0},"close":{"day":2,"hour":15,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":3,"hour":9,"minute":0},"close":{"day":3,"hour":15,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":4,"hour":9,"minute":0},"close":{"day":4,"hour":15,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":5,"hour":9,"minute":0},"close":{"day":5,"hour":15,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":6,"hour":9,"minute":0},"close":{"day":6,"hour":15,"minute":0}}],"weekdayDescriptions":["Monday: 9:00 AM – 3:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 3:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 3:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 3:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 3:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 3:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 3:00 PM"],"nextOpenTime":"2026-02-16T15:00:00Z"},"userRatingCount":621,"displayName":{"text":"Living Sky Café","languageCode":"en"},"primaryTypeDisplayName":{"text":"Restaurant","languageCode":"en-US"},"editorialSummary":{"text":"Cosy outpost offering hearty breakfast & lunch standards alongside pastries, sweets & coffee drinks.","languageCode":"en"},"reviews":[{"name":"places/ChIJsd8Recb2BFMRgtZcHAsmc9Q/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pocE4xSjZNazFhU3pGUFVHaHZUMEZwTWpSbFFtYxAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"3 months ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"Incredibly fresh and tasty! The food was delicious and the drinks were a delight!\n\nThe syrup for the drinks and the dipping for the fries all felt like it was home made.\n\nTo top it off, our server was also very attentive to our order. She knew exactly who order what and without asking she would serve each person their order!\n\nDefinitely gonna come back when we get the chance!","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"Incredibly fresh and tasty! The food was delicious and the drinks were a delight!\n\nThe syrup for the drinks and the dipping for the fries all felt like it was home made.\n\nTo top it off, our server was also very attentive to our order. She knew exactly who order what and without asking she would serve each person their order!\n\nDefinitely gonna come back when we get the chance!","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Munin Kim","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108366396521549496176/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkhB57pZRY9PhLrvAzlySJ-9vehvlXlDIhx8uyJ_feDsBdwkrfSQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"},"publishTime":"2025-10-26T19:15:55.912698787Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pocE4xSjZNazFhU3pGUFVHaHZUMEZwTWpSbFFtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pocE4xSjZNazFhU3pGUFVHaHZUMEZwTWpSbFFtYxAB!2m1!1s0x5304f6c67911dfb1:0xd473260b1c5cd682"},{"name":"places/ChIJsd8Recb2BFMRgtZcHAsmc9Q/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsaFRHeHhjRk13TFhSemJIcE1WM3B1UVc5TUxWRRAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"2 months ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"We visited Living Sky while staying in downtown Saskatoon and it was worth the chilly walk!\n\nI had the chicken & waffles and let me TELL YOU. One of the best I've ever had. The contrast between the egg fried in chili oil with the sweet crunchy toasted coconut was amazing. The portion is one egg and waffle, I was worried it may not be enough but it was so filling - the perfect amount! I also had the vanilla bean latte which was awesome and not too sweet.\n\nThere is a 100% chance we will be back next visit. Also the hostess and our server Sarah S were absolutely lovely and really enhanced our experience!","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"We visited Living Sky while staying in downtown Saskatoon and it was worth the chilly walk!\n\nI had the chicken & waffles and let me TELL YOU. One of the best I've ever had. The contrast between the egg fried in chili oil with the sweet crunchy toasted coconut was amazing. The portion is one egg and waffle, I was worried it may not be enough but it was so filling - the perfect amount! I also had the vanilla bean latte which was awesome and not too sweet.\n\nThere is a 100% chance we will be back next visit. Also the hostess and our server Sarah S were absolutely lovely and really enhanced our experience!","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Devonny Hadder","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105605846368609761104/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4q3F2iVhz4PZHGbTQyCwzb-irp260vrYxXDA16LBCvTj4Vnt0=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"},"publishTime":"2025-12-11T17:47:56.244902694Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsaFRHeHhjRk13TFhSemJIcE1WM3B1UVc5TUxWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsaFRHeHhjRk13TFhSemJIcE1WM3B1UVc5TUxWRRAB!2m1!1s0x5304f6c67911dfb1:0xd473260b1c5cd682"},{"name":"places/ChIJsd8Recb2BFMRgtZcHAsmc9Q/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xVGRGRlNjRzVoT1MweGFHczNVRXB1YW05dFUzYxAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"3 months ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"Shelby, who served me was kind and engaging. A compliment to the inviting nature of the space. Small, closely - placed booths and tables create a sense of community.\nThe mushroom soup is perfect on this brisk November morning. A roasted beet wrap with candied pecans! Where else am I going to find that on a menu? A Warm and earthy combination with arugula and caramelized onions. Kettle chips on the side offer a touch of salt and a crunch that completes the meal in a casually classy way. Don’t forget the honey- cinnamon syrup in your favorite coffee drink.","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"Shelby, who served me was kind and engaging. A compliment to the inviting nature of the space. Small, closely - placed booths and tables create a sense of community.\nThe mushroom soup is perfect on this brisk November morning. A roasted beet wrap with candied pecans! Where else am I going to find that on a menu? A Warm and earthy combination with arugula and caramelized onions. Kettle chips on the side offer a touch of salt and a crunch that completes the meal in a casually classy way. Don’t forget the honey- cinnamon syrup in your favorite coffee drink.","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Em H","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104144041230316620725/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4FkqIiRgxZSlY7JQwiry8sEbY6yy18Gi8ZX7d7oviQ00DPo_4vA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"},"publishTime":"2025-11-06T18:30:10.764490337Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xVGRGRlNjRzVoT1MweGFHczNVRXB1YW05dFUzYxAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xVGRGRlNjRzVoT1MweGFHczNVRXB1YW05dFUzYxAB!2m1!1s0x5304f6c67911dfb1:0xd473260b1c5cd682"},{"name":"places/ChIJsd8Recb2BFMRgtZcHAsmc9Q/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2toMVNrZHlRbUZZY1ZJemRFaGFUV0ozT0daNVRtYxAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"2 months ago","rating":4,"text":{"text":"My meal was fantastic. Small portion. Cute store. Great service! Love the Caesar but they could use a bit of a larger menu for drinks!\n\nTried my momma’s was a bit too “healthy/natural” for me, but if you are into that you will love it!","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"My meal was fantastic. Small portion. Cute store. Great service! Love the Caesar but they could use a bit of a larger menu for drinks!\n\nTried my momma’s was a bit too “healthy/natural” for me, but if you are into that you will love it!","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"California","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111070386167388001559/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV86ki5odkwNtQ5b60WBlaGP-vj_gBnGqKIARY83NCUpAvxMhwQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"},"publishTime":"2025-12-02T18:04:36.237447918Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2toMVNrZHlRbUZZY1ZJemRFaGFUV0ozT0daNVRtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2toMVNrZHlRbUZZY1ZJemRFaGFUV0ozT0daNVRtYxAB!2m1!1s0x5304f6c67911dfb1:0xd473260b1c5cd682"},{"name":"places/ChIJsd8Recb2BFMRgtZcHAsmc9Q/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25FemFFMVVPRGMzTjJWZk9FaHFNMFJqU1ZkNGExRRAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"3 months ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"Wonderful experience! We ordered the sticky situation and the wild mushroom burger for lunch. The burgers were so flavourful and delicious! Can’t wait to come back and try more. Thanks so much Jackie for the great service! :)","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"Wonderful experience! We ordered the sticky situation and the wild mushroom burger for lunch. The burgers were so flavourful and delicious! Can’t wait to come back and try more. Thanks so much Jackie for the great service! :)","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Athena Ranger","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109417554961880373365/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKV90y6wzbHcuBnTuQKcpUdpDSYPJEgIDMxtlZoyEIvSPG_bQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2025-11-09T21:21:45.721111050Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUN